lyrics:
[Verse 1]
They say Rockstar's got the magic touch
Creating worlds that thrill us so much
But why is GTA 6 taking forever to arrive
Leaving us longing, barely alive

[Chorus]
Oh Rockstar, tell us, what's the deal
We need our fix, it's time to reveal
Bring on GTA 6, our hearts ache
This wait is more than we can take
